name: March 2 Infinity - Dunes of Aspirations I
description:
Dunes of Aspirations.

"Has ‘humanity’ started the path on our journey to ‘infinity’ ?
Barren lands have to be explored to find the black stones of forbidden knowledge.
What will this journey bring us? 
Generations doomed for the eternal search for what once was taken for granted ?
When will we become gods again ?"


1/1 Duo Paintings - 1 Traditional and 1 VQGAN based upon that traditional.

By Sedas. Part of Art Series - March 2 Infinity - The March to Infinity had departed. Will Humanity make the right choices ? 
See our website - https://mod.sedas.be/artseries/
